<div class="processSubhead">Reaction Kinetics</div>
<div class="mini" style="margin-top:6px; margin-bottom:14px;">Maps the sample temperature history to pyrolytic conversion Î±(t) using Arrhenius-based reaction kinetics k(T), expressed in both rate and integral forms.</div>
<div class="eqBox eqKinetics">
<div class="eqMath latex" data-display="true" data-latex="\begin{aligned}
\frac{d\alpha}{dt} &amp;= k(T)\,(1-\alpha) \\[10pt]
k(T) &amp;= A_1\,\exp\!\left(\frac{-E_a}{R\,T}\right) \\[12pt]
\alpha(t) &amp;= 1-\exp\!\left(-\int_{0}^{t}k\!\left(T(\tau)\right)\,d\tau\right)
\end{aligned}">
</div>
<div class="eqKey">
<div class="eqKeyTitle">Key</div>
<div class="eqKeyList">
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="\alpha"></span><span class="eqDefinition">fractional conversion of dry feed</span></div>
