<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="T"></span><span class="eqDefinition">sample temperature (K)</span></div>
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="k(T)"></span><span class="eqDefinition">temperature-dependent rate constant (sâ»Â¹)</span></div>
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="A_1"></span><span class="eqDefinition">pre-exponential factor (sâ»Â¹) (stored internally unless measured)</span></div>
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="E_a"></span><span class="eqDefinition">activation energy (J/mol) (stored internally unless measured)</span></div>
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="R"></span><span class="eqDefinition">gas constant, 8.314 J/mol/K (stored internally unless measured)</span></div>
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="\tau"></span><span class="eqDefinition">integration dummy time (s)</span></div>
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="T(\tau)"></span><span class="eqDefinition">sample temperature history (K)</span></div>
<div><span class="k latex" data-display="false" data-latex="\int_0^t k(T(\tau))\,d\tau"></span><span class="eqDefinition">dimensionless accumulated reaction severity</span></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
