      '================ VACUUM PYROLYSIS CYCLE ================',
      'Dry feed per run:                         '+fmt(feed,3)+' g',
      'Active carbon/polymer pyrolysis run:       '+fmt(runLow,2)+'-'+fmt(runHigh,2)+' hr',
